metadata.name: Official NFT autograph. Vasyl Virastyuk.
metadata.description: Official NFT autograph — Vasyl Virastyuk, the strongest man on the planet in 2004 and 2007. You can verify its originality by watching the interview with him and his official FB page, where he confirms that he autographs for the Philography NFT project. According to reputable online media, the athlete is among the top 10 strongest men in the world in mankind’s history.
